    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(SN) In nomine Domini. Millesimo C quadragesirno II, XIII kalendas marcii,
                        indicione V. <rs key="#Monasteries #Abbots">Cenobio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName>, sito inter Padum novem et veterem. Nos <persName
                            key="#childOf #Lombard #Offersio/donatio #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                            >Rubeo</persName> de <placeName ref="#places/2418"
                        >Guvernulo</placeName>, <rs key="#childOf">filiia</rs> quondam <persName
                            key="#parentOf #Lombard">Wiberti</persName> de
                            <placeName>Plaza</placeName>, et <persName
                            key="#Lombard #Offersio/donatio #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                            >Gerardum</persName> filii <persName key="#Lombard">Literii</persName>
                        et <persName
                            key="#siblingOf #childOf #Lombard #Offersio/donatio #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                            >Bernardum</persName> et <persName
                            key="#siblingOf #childOf #Lombard #Offersio/donatio #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                            >Bruxatum</persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf #Lombard">germanis</rs>, filii quondam <persName
                            key="#parentOf">Vualterii</persName> de Plaza, *** qui professus sum ex
                        nacione nostra lege [vi]vere <rs key="#Lombard">Longobardorum</rs>,
                        offertores et donatores ipsius monasterii presentes presentibus diximus:
                        quisquis in sanctis ac in venerabilibus locis ex suis aliquid contulerit
                        rebus iusta hoctoris vocem, in hoc seculo centuplum accipiet, insuper, quod
                        melius est, vitam possidebit eternam. Ideoque nos supranorninati donamus et
                        obferrimus a presenti die in eadem monasterii, pro mercede anime nostre et
                        parentum nostrorum, tempore <persName key="#Abbots #Monasteries"
                            ref="#people/3570">Wigelmi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs>, silicet <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals">pecies de terra aratoria</rs>
                        que iacet in <placeName
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Roads #Forests"
                            >Piscarola</placeName>. Fines: a mane <rs key="#Roads">via</rs>, a
                        meridie <placeName>Supragnacula</placeName>, a sera obfertores, de subto <rs
                            key="#Forests">bosco</rs>, sibi que sunt coerentes. Quas pecias supra ab
                        hac die eidem monasterio Sancti Benedicti donamus et offerrimus et per
                        presentem <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">cartam offersionis</rs> ibidem abendum
                        confirmamus sine nostra et heredum nostrorum contradicione. Equidem
                        spondimus atque promittimus: nos suprnc Rubeus et Gerardus et Bernardus et
                        Bruxatus, una cum nostris heredibus, iamscriptam cartam offersionis nostre
                        qualiter superius legitur in integrum ab omni homine defendere; quod si
                        defendere non potuerimus, aut si parti ipsius monasterii exinde aliquid per
                        quodvis ingenium subtraere quesierimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in
                            duplum</rs> eandem cartam parti ipsius monasterii restituamus in
                        consimili loco. Actum in loco <placeName ref="#places/2469"
                            >Campaniola</placeName>. Feliciter. + Signum manibus + <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio">Capo de Lupi</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name>Sachello</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio #childOf"><name ref="Albertus"
                                >Alberto</name></persName> filius <persName key="#parentOf"
                                ><name>Arnaldo</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="/de Nuvelare"
                                >Gandulfo</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/462"
                            >Nuvelare</placeName> et <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name>Ubaldo Palario</name></persName> rogati sunt <rs
                            key="#Witness">testes</rs>. + Signum manibus + Rubeus et Gerardus et
                        Bernardus et Bruxatus ***, qui hanc cartam offersionis fieret firmare
                        rogavit ut supra. + Signum + <rs key="#Writer">Scripsi</rs> ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary #Offersio/donatio">Gerardus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> sacri palacii post tradita complevi et dedi. </ab>
